text:
Thanks, Juri. You've been looking after
everyone's needs, haven't you?

Huh? I haven't done anything special...
Just the usual, like always.

...but if I'm still doing what I've always done...
I'm doing as well as I can...
It's probably because everyone is here.

Haha... You must be tired too, Juri.
If you're sleepy, you can go to bed too.
Yawn... Yeah, maybe I'll do that──

Thanks to you, Producer,
it's been a great training camp.
